</div>

<div class="callout">

    <p>1xBet betting company conducts the "Express of the Day" campaign on a permanent basis. Daily express trains from popular events are automatically compiled on the site, and experts work on analyzing matches and making high-quality forecasts. If the express chosen by the client turns out to be a winning one, then the BC accrues +10% to the final coefficient.
    </p>
    <p>Every day 2 types of already assembled express appear on the main page of the site:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Live - here are the events that have already started when you visited</li>
        <li>Line - here are bets on those matches that have not started yet
        </li>
    </ul>

<p class='center'>
