    <p>The Express of the day includes various sporting events, you can bet on three or more. If you like this offer, then rather top up your coupon or choose the one that suits you best. Every day 1xBet collects from 5 to 10 expresses for Live and for the Line. Each coupon contains a sport, a match, the name of the championship, a bet or a coefficient, usually 3 events are included in the coupon.</p>

